tafsir[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"Alla woondirii naange e waktu ɓamtaraade nge ka fuɗirde mannge.,"
  91,2,"O woondiri lewru sondu rewii batte henge caggal mutal."
  91,3,"O woondiri ñalawma sombo hunciima e dow yeeso leydi e njalbeendi hembo."
  91,4,"Mi woondiri jemma si mbo muuri laral leydi, ndi wonta niɓɓundi."
  91,5,"O woondiri kammu, O woondiri mahngo mammbo haralla."
  91,6,"O woondiri leydi, O woondiri mbertu mayri, ngam aade en koɗa heen."
  91,7,"O woondiri kala fittaandu, O woondiri tagde Alla ndu fittaandu fotondirndu."
  91,8,"O fammini ndu ko aldah e jannginde ko boni ndu deesto, e ko laba ndu waɗa."
  91,9,"Malaama oon laɓɓinɗo fittaandu mum o suɗi ndu e ɓure, o ittindu e ko boni."
  91,10,"Pertii tigi oon loowɗo fittaandu makko e goopi e bakkatuuji."
  91,11,"Samuud en pennii annabi mum en Saalih sabu yawtude ɓe keerol e waɗde goopi e bakkatuuji."
  91,12,"Tumo nde ɓurɗo hiiteede e mum en ummii caggal neleede mbo ummaade e yimɓe mum en."
  91,13,"Nelaaɗo mum en Saalih maakani ɓe: Accee naaga Alla,e yarde ba ñalawma mabba wotee memnee ba bonannde."
  91,14,"ɓe penni nelaaɓe mum en ko faati e ngelooba he, ɓurɗo o hiiteede wari ba e weleedeɓe, ɓe ndenndi bakkaat, Alla ommbi e mum en lepte Makko, O halkari ɓe haacaanga sabu bakkatuui mum en, O fotndi ɓe lepte ɗe O halkari ɓe."
  91,15,"Alla waɗi e mum en lepte kalkuɗe ɓe, te O hulaani kanko Ceniiɗo O battane mum."
